<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="24Jun1920"><font color="red">24 June 1920</font>, <cite>NYPL</cite> (JJ to John Quinn): I shall send you tomorrow five chapters or episodes, <cite>Wandering Rocks</cite>, <cite>Sirens</cite>, <cite>Cyclops</cite>, <cite>Nausikaa</cite> and <cite>Oxen of the Sun</cite> and a few days later nine more, making entire MS so far. The final adventure and close of the book I shall remit you as written during the next few months &hellip; [Joyce also asked Quinn to cable an additional advance on receipt c/o Thomas Cook and Sons, Paris,] or, if you prefer, the balance of the total price.</div>
